{{作品名稱|name=''The Tree of Life''|hk=生命樹|tw=永生樹|cn=生命之树}}是[[泰倫斯·馬利克|泰倫斯·馬利克]]自编自导的2011年美国[[劇情片|劇情片]]，[[畢·彼特|畢·彼特]]、[[西恩·潘|西恩·潘]]、[[杰西卡·查斯坦|杰西卡·查斯坦]]主演，彼特是本片制片人。潘扮演中年建筑师杰克回首童年往事，以此探究生命的起源和意义。他质疑自身信仰，想要找到存在的目标，同时尝试理解和接受霸道的父亲（皮特饰），与母亲的关系一直不温不火。[[亚历山大·德斯普拉|亚历山大·德斯普拉]]为本片作曲，[[艾曼纽尔·卢贝兹基|艾曼纽尔·卢贝兹基]]任摄影指导。<ref name="TOLNYT">{{cite news | accessdate = 2021-06-09 | last = Scott | first = A. O. | archivedate = 2021-03-22 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/27/movies/the-tree-of-life-from-terrence-malick-review.html?pagewanted=all | title = Heaven, Texas and the Cosmic Whodunit | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 2011-05-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210322130510/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/27/movies/the-tree-of-life-from-terrence-malick-review.html?pagewanted=all}}</ref><ref name="TOLRT">{{cite web | title = The Tree of Life | access-date = 2021-06-09 | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_tree_of_life_2011 | archive-date = 2021-03-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210316084827/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_tree_of_life_2011 | dead-url = no | work = Rotten Tomatoes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2018-07-01 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/tree-life-review/ | title = The Tree Of Life Review | work = [[帝國雜誌|Empire]] | last = Nathan | first = Ian | date = 2011-06-27 | accessdate = 2021-06-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180701061404/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/tree-life/review/}}</ref>

电影摄制预算约3200万美元<ref name="BOMTOL">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-01-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210125224510/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt0478304/ | title = The Tree of Life (2011) | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt0478304/ | access-date = 2021-06-09}}</ref>，2011年5月16日在[[第64届戛纳电影节|第64届戛纳电影节]]首映<ref>{{cite news | first = Dennis | archivedate = 2020-11-12 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/22/movies/the-tree-of-life-premieres-at-cannes.html | title = Pursuing Imperfection in Malick’s Eden | work = The New York Times | last = Lim | date = 2011-05-16 | accessdate = 2021-06-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002739/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/22/movies/the-tree-of-life-premieres-at-cannes.html | dead-url = no}}</ref>，影评人评论两极分化<ref>{{cite news | date = 2011-05-16 | accessdate = 2021-06-09 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/may/16/cannes-2011-terrence-malick-tree-life | title = Cannes 2011: Terrence Malick's The Tree of Life is talk of the town | work = [[衛報|The Guardian]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210606095001/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/may/16/cannes-2011-terrence-malick-tree-life | last = Higgins | first = Charlotte | archivedate = 2021-06-06 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/brad-pitts-tree-life-sets-188621/ | title = Brad Pitt's 'Tree of Life' Sets Off Mixed Frenzy of Boos, Applause (Cannes 2011) | work = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | last = Kilday | first = Gregg | date = 2011-05-16 | accessdate = 2021-06-09 | archivedate = 2020-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201102182453/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/brad-pitts-tree-life-sets-188621 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。《生命之树》2011年5月27日开始院线发行，全球票房5840万美元<ref name="TOLRT" /><ref name="BOMTOL" />。[[汇总媒体|评论汇总]]网站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]共收集本片289篇评论，认可度达八成四<ref name="TOLRT" />。影评入围上百奖项，胜出六十余项，涉及领域全面开花，导演、编剧、摄影、剪辑、视觉效果、配乐、皮特与查